131
00:11:06,780 --> 00:11:12,420
So the original overlap proclaimed 
by Dawkins of 98.5 percent is not  

132
00:11:12,420 --> 00:11:15,600
close to reality. As our knowledge about human and  

133
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:20,580
